data.description: Don't miss this adorable house. It sits at the base of the South Mountains. The hiking trails are calling you & they are just across the street! Fresh interior. Formal Dining Room. Bonus/Rec room with newly installed Steel & Glass cabinets! NO HOA.  Sizeable lot with plenty of room to park some toys, or have that big family reunion. Drive on in the Double RV Gate & park in the DETACHED, ALL METAL GARAGE with a WORKSHOP inside...18' X 30'...and it has electricity! Newly painted interior & exterior. Enjoy the Ma-Ha Tuak City Park down the street. Take in the beautiful sunsets from the front yard. Did I mention NO HOA? Spray-in attic insulation added 10 months ago to help beat down those hot summer electric bills!
